<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungsietna a kihawm ie!
 Chitin leh namtin te di'n;
 Hukdampa naka put chu,
 Hehpihna lopi ahi.

[V2]
 Gilo, gimthei liengvaite,
 Lungsietna gam nuom chang ui;
 Thisan thieng taka ei tat zalin,
 A nuom tapoh in zuon un.

[V3]
 2. Lungsietna hun sung ahin,
 Lut unla, gamnuom chang un;
 Na gitlohnau cheng pumin,
 Hukdampa'n silthieng ina.

[V4]
 3. Gamtiem chang dinga guotsa,
 Gammang lo hiel din chieh tau;
 Sapna Aw chu ngaiphau in,
 Kanaan gam Lalpa ahi.

[V5]
 4. Nunnawp Aw gi chu ka zai,
 Vak lopi ka muh phatin;
 Ka suihlung lawpna'n a dim,
 Thisan lul tatna ziekin.</lyrics>
<title>Repentance To The Lord</title>
<hymn_number>131</hymn_number>
</song>